Timeline: Library Management System - 2 Person Team
---------------------------------------------------

Week 1 (April 15 – April 21)
✔ Project setup
   - Create GitHub repo, .gitignore, README, project board
   - Choose interface type (CLI or GUI)
   - Assign roles and agree on workflow
✔ Phase 1 - Models
   - Implement Book.java
   - Implement Borrower.java

Week 2 (April 22 – April 25)
✔ Phase 2 - Services
