✔ Phase 3 - File Handling
   - Create FileHandler.java
   - Implement reading/writing books.txt and borrowers.txt

April 26 (Friday)
✔ Phase 4 - Interface
   - Complete CLI or GUI interface
   - Integrate with LibraryService

April 27 (Saturday)
✔ Testing & Polish
   - Full functionality test
